description:
The game works only with devices starting from iPhone 6S, iPhone 6 Plus, iPad Mini 5, iPad Air 3, iPhone SE and older!

Greet the driver Michalych, he dreams of conquering the mountains of the whole world, he is smart, understands machines and sometimes jokes.

Get ready, you will find a variety of equipment and extreme maps. Collect bonuses on the map to unlock new cars, tuning and maps. On the maps you are waiting for mud puddles, crossing the river, traps, various items, missions and much more!

- Realistic physics and graphics with settings;
- Many different modes for every taste;
- Many different vehicles, from Kafer to tracked all-terrain vehicle;
- Picturesque cards with their own secrets and easter eggs;
- Mars! Real Mars is waiting for you! How do you like it, Musk?
- Interesting maps: Chernobyl, Everest, Taiga, Devil's Island, and more.
- Tuning cars, the plot for Michalych and various missions;

